data.description: Contemporary 4/2.5 home in Walnut Grove Lake! This Naturalistic designed home features large viewing windows & sliding doors and a layout surrounding a center atrium. Formal living and great room both have stone fireplaces, original wood floors & covered patios. 3rd covered patio in back leads to the hot tub. Two car carport w 2 large storage closets. New carpets, kitchen appliances stay. Lake access across street @ park. Seller Home Warranty with First American has been purchased, Selling As Is
